    <div class="content"><p>Thank you for saying this. Text is much more consumable than audio, which is much more consumable than video. I would also like to add that using video excludes blind and deaf people from your content. Text can be understood by anyone from Superman to Helen Keller. Video and audio cannot.</p>
</div>
